# User ALSA defaults. Loaded through ~/.asoundrc, not ALSA_CONFIG_PATH.
# Do not override pcm.!default or ctl.!default here: each platform's system
# ALSA config remains authoritative. Explicit hw: devices stay available when
# supported; that does not imply automatic fallback from a PipeWire default.

